00:11:41.272 --> 00:11:44.375
Whether Hua Yong is staying at
the hospital, or who he's visiting...

00:11:45.076 --> 00:11:46.277
What does it matter to you?

00:11:46.744 --> 00:11:47.611
Shen Wenlang.

00:11:47.612 --> 00:11:49.547
