standing next to you.

00:11:55.386 --> 00:11:57.454
You think you can take advantage of me?

00:11:57.455 --> 00:11:58.455
Oh.

00:11:59.090 --> 00:12:01.092
Well, you can come over here and try.

00:12:01.425 --> 00:12:02.093
Wenlang.

00:12:02.326 --> 00:12:04.428
