I think it's hemorrhagic shock.

00:13:14.832 --> 00:13:15.766
We need to save him now.

00:13:15.766 --> 00:13:16.434
Emergency blood transfusion required.

00:13:16.434 --> 00:13:17.401
What's his blood type?

00:13:17.402 --> 00:13:18.836
He's an S-class Alpha like me

00:13:19.003 --> 00:13:19.970
I think it's type A.

00:13:19.971 --> 00:13:21.638
Okay, I'll call the blood bank and
get a transfusion ready right away.

00:13:21.639 --> 00:13:22.639
Wait a minute, Doctor.

00:13:23.174 --> 00:13:23.741
My boss

00:13:24.108 --> 00:13:25.108
